Antifungal activity of montmorillonite/peptide aptamer nanocomposite against 
Colletotrichum gloeosporioides on Stylosanthes.

Xu Z(1), Jiang X(1), Li Y(2), Ma X(1), Tang Y(1), Li H(1), Yi K(2), Li J(3), Liu 
Z(4).

Author information:
(1)School of Life Sciences, Hainan University, Haikou 570228, China; One Health 
Insititute, Hainan University, Haikou 570228, China.
(2)Environment and Plant Protection Institute, Chinese Academy of Tropical 
Agricultural Sciences, Haikou 571101, China.
(3)School of Life Sciences, Hainan University, Haikou 570228, China; One Health 
Insititute, Hainan University, Haikou 570228, China. Electronic address: 
lijuanjuan@hainanu.edu.cn.
(4)School of Life Sciences, Hainan University, Haikou 570228, China; One Health 
Insititute, Hainan University, Haikou 570228, China. Electronic address: 
