Lipodystrophy-associated progeroid syndromes.

Araújo-Vilar D(1)(2), Fernández-Pombo A(3)(4), Cobelo-Gómez S(3), Castro 
AI(4)(5), Sánchez-Iglesias S(3).

Author information:
(1)UETeM-Molecular Pathology Group, Department of Psychiatry, Radiology, Public 
Health, Nursing and Medicine (Medicine Area), Center for Research in Molecular 
Medicine and Chronic Diseases (CIMUS)-IDIS, University of Santiago de 
Compostela, 15782, Santiago de Compostela, Spain. david.araujo@usc.es.
(2)Division of Endocrinology and Nutrition, University Clinical Hospital of 
Santiago de Compostela, 15706, Santiago de Compostela, Spain. 
david.araujo@usc.es.
(3)UETeM-Molecular Pathology Group, Department of Psychiatry, Radiology, Public 
Health, Nursing and Medicine (Medicine Area), Center for Research in Molecular 
